headline: Essex Property Rewards Investors With Another Annual Dividend Hike
summary: ESS lifts its annual dividend for the 32nd straight year, raising the payout to $10.36 per share as solid FFO growth and liquidity back returns.

headline: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish on Essex Property Trust Stock?
summary: As Essex Property Trust has underperformed relative to the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a cautious outlook about the stock’s prospects.
